DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({2019}, 'Date'[Year])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Product'[Brand])),
			NOT('Product'[Brand] IN {"Southridge Video",
				"Tailspin Toys"})
		)

EVALUATE
	SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(__DS0FilterTable, __DS0FilterTable2, "FVERSION", IGNORE('DAX'[FVERSION]))

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({2019}, 'Date'[Year])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Product'[Brand])),
			NOT('Product'[Brand] IN {"Southridge Video",
				"Tailspin Toys"})
		)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Product'[Brand],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__DS0FilterTable2,
			"Sales_Amount", 'DAX'[Sales Amount]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(1001, __DS0Core, [Sales_Amount], 0, 'Product'[Brand], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[Sales_Amount] DESC, 'Product'[Brand]

metrics.visualTitle: Sales Amount by Brand and Continent

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({2019}, 'Date'[Year])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Product'[Brand])),
			NOT('Product'[Brand] IN {"Southridge Video",
				"Tailspin Toys"})
		)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Product'[Brand],
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('Customer'[Continent], "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"),
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__DS0FilterTable2,
			"Sales_Amount", 'DAX'[Sales Amount]
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = FALSE)),
			"'Product'[Brand]", 'Product'[Brand],
			"'Customer'[Continent]", 'Customer'[Continent],
			"Sales_Amount", [Sales_Amount]
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM0 = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = TRUE)),
			"'Product'[Brand]", 'Product'[Brand],
			"SortBy_DM0_0", [Sales_Amount]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Product'[Brand]),
			__DS0CoreTableByDM0
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(201, __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns, [SortBy_DM0_0], 0, 'Product'[Brand], 1)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals, 'Customer'[Continent])

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(62, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'Customer'[Continent], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryWindowed,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'Customer'[Continent],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'Customer'[Continent]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[SortBy_DM0_0] DESC, 'Product'[Brand], [ColumnIndex]
